    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in solid shape and has plenty of life left for all your upcoming adventures! It\u2019s been well-maintained and is super reliable for daily commutes or weekend getaways. I'm looking for someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
