    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. This example exhibits excellent linear power delivery and the characteristic induction note of its individual throttle bodies. To address common platform weaknesses, the rear subframe has been structurally reinforced, and the VANOS system has been recently overhauled to ensure precise variable valve timing. The M-Variable limited-slip differential provides consistent lock-up for corner-exit traction, while the suspension retains its factory-intended damping characteristics and turn-in response. Recent service includes a full valve adjustment and cooling system refresh, making this a turn-key enthusiast vehicle optimized for driver engagement.",
