    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of pride of ownership, balancing spirited performance with everyday utility. The exterior maintains a deep, lustrous shine, though a keen eye might find minor surface blemishes consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free sanctuary of comfort; the premium seating surfaces are supple and free of tears, and every button, dial, and digital display functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is exceptionally sound, having recently undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection and a fresh oil service. The engine delivers smooth, responsive power, while the transmission shifts seamlessly through every gear. It has been primarily garage-kept and strictly maintained according to the manufacturer's recommended schedule. Whether you are looking for a dependable daily commuter or a refined weekend cruiser, this car offers a driving experience that feels tight and well-composed. It comes complete with a full set of keys, floor mats, and all original owner\u2019s manuals.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
