      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) features the refined 3.6L M96 flat-six with VarioCam Plus, delivering linear power through a crisp 6-speed G96 manual transaxle. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a factory-spec McPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension that tracks with surgical precision. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh Rear Main Seal. While the finish shows honest road wear consistent with its mileage, the mechanical vitals\u2014from the compression-tested cylinders to the responsive hydraulic steering rack\u2014are in robust health. A driver-focused example ready for technical canyon work.",
